text: __NOTOC__ Year 266 (CCLXVI) was a common year starting on Monday of the Julian calendar. == Events == === By place === ==== Roman Empire ==== * King Odaenathus of Palmyra invades Persia. He takes the capital Ctesiphon. He gives himself with the title "king of kings". ==== Ireland ==== * The rule of High King Cormac mac Airt ends (approximate date). == Births == * Wang Dun, general of the Jin Dynasty (d. 324) == Deaths == * Category:260s
